name: DecodeBatchDiagnostics
summary: Aggregated diagnostics for a batch decode run.

properties.name: Total
properties.summary: Gets total number of inputs processed.

properties.name: Success
properties.summary: Gets the number of successful decodes.

properties.name: InvalidInput
properties.summary: Gets the number of invalid input failures.

properties.name: UnsupportedFormat
properties.summary: Gets the number of unsupported format failures.

properties.name: Cancelled
properties.summary: Gets the number of cancelled decodes.

properties.name: NoResult
properties.summary: Gets the number of no-result decodes.

properties.name: Error
properties.summary: Gets the number of unexpected errors.

properties.name: TotalElapsed
properties.summary: Gets the total elapsed time across all items.

properties.name: FailureCount
properties.summary: Gets the number of failed decodes.

properties.name: AverageElapsed
properties.summary: Gets the average elapsed time per item.
